&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/APAC-SEOUL-SAMWONG-GARDEN-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-4602&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/APAC-SEOUL-SAMWONG-GARDEN-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;APAC- SEOUL- SAMWONG GARDEN- OFFER- LOGO MEDIUM&quot; width=&quot;144&quot; height=&quot;30&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Located in the fashionable Gangnam district of Seoul, Samwon Garden is a massive restaurant with interior dining room of traditional style and outdoor seating in a peaceful garden setting with waterfall and fishpond. Serving authentic, traditional Korean cuisine cooked at your table on a grill, Samwon Garden is the setting for many state dinners and is enjoyed by locals and visitors alike. Casual attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contact Samwon Garden by phone at +82 2 548 3030 or email at info@samwongarden.com to book your reservation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, the date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number and your email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No reconfirmation is necessary. As a courtesy, please provide with restaurant with 24 hours&rsquo; notice if cancellation is necessary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on Availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Restaurant Merchant&lt;/p&gt;

